@DATABASE "Twin Turbo V8"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - T - Twin Turbo V8"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - T
                   ====================================

                               Twin Turbo V8
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42006,99)"}          42006,x (x= 1-99)
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(49759,0)"}          49759,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
